quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,100,"Sọ pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé ẹ̀yin l’ẹ ni ìkápá lórí àwọn ilé ọrọ̀ ìkẹ́ Olúwa mi ni, nígbà náà ẹ̀yin ìbá diwọ́ mọ́ ọn ní ti ìbẹ̀rù òṣì. Ènìyàn sì jẹ́ ahun."
  17,101,"Dájúdájú A fún (Ànábì) Mūsā ní àwọn àmì mẹ́sàn-án tó yanjú. Bi àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl léèrè wò. Rántí, nígbà tí ó dé ọ̀dọ̀ wọn, Fir‘aon wí fún un pé: “Dájúdájú èmi lérò pé eléèdì ni ọ́, Mūsā.”"
  17,102,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “O kúkú mọ̀ pé kò sí ẹni tí ó sọ àwọn (àmì) wọ̀nyí kalẹ̀ bí kò ṣe Olúwa àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀; (ó sì jẹ́) ìmọ̀ àmọ̀dájú àti ẹ̀rí. Dájúdájú èmi náà lérò pé ẹni ìparun ni ọ́, Fir‘aon.”"
  18,67,"(Kidr) sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ìwọ kò lè ṣe sùúrù pẹ̀lú mi."
  18,68,"Àti pé báwo ni o ṣe máa ṣe sùúrù lórí ohun tí o ò fi ìmọ̀ rọkiri ká rẹ̀?”"
  18,69,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Tí Allāhu bá fẹ́, ó máa bá mi ní onísùúrù. Èmi kò sì níí yapa àṣẹ rẹ.”"
  19,28,"Arábìnrin Hārūn, bàbá rẹ kì í ṣe ènìyàn burúkú. Àti pé ìyá rẹ kì í ṣe alágbèrè.”"
  19,29,"Ó sì tọ́ka sí ọmọ náà. Wọ́n sọ pé: “Báwo ni a ó ṣe bá ẹni tó wà lórí ìtẹ́, tó jẹ́ ọmọ òpóǹló sọ̀rọ̀?”"
  19,30,"(Ọmọ náà) sọ̀rọ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú ẹrú Allāhu ni èmi. (Allāhu) fún mi ní Tírà. Ó sì ṣe mí ní Ànábì.{1}.",1:[Ẹrú Allāhu ni Ànábì ‘Īsā ọmọ Mọryam - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -, àmọ́ àwọn nasọ̄rọ̄ kò gbàgbọ́ pé ẹrú Allāhu ni.]
  20,10,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó rí iná kan, ó sọ fún àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ pé: “Ẹ dúró síbí. Dájúdájú èmi rí iná kan. Ó ṣeé ṣe kí n̄g rí ògúnná mú wá fún yín nínú rẹ̀ tàbí kí n̄g rí ojú ọ̀nà kan nítòsí iná náà.”"
  20,11,"Nígbà tí ó dé ibẹ̀, A pè é “Mūsā,"
  20,12,"Dájúdájú Èmi ni Olúwa rẹ. Nítorí náà, bọ́ bàtà rẹ méjèèjì sílẹ̀.{1} Dájúdájú ìwọ wà ní àfonífojì mímọ́, Tuwā..",1:[Ìdí tí Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - fi pa á láṣẹ fún Ànábì Mūsā - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - láti bọ́ bàtà ẹsẹ̀ rẹ̀ sílẹ̀, gẹ́gẹ́ bí ọmọ Mọs‘ūd - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí i - ṣe gbà á wá ni pé, awọ òkúǹbete kẹ́tẹ́kẹ́tẹ́ tí wọn kò pa lósè ni wọ́n fi ṣe bàtà náà.]
